    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like \"intuition\" though. like, it's not a gut feeling, it's actually like I'm seeing a ghost of the event stuck to the object. i could see the light hitting the cracks in the vase in a way that felt... i don't know, wrong. like it was reflecting a light that hadn't happened yet. it feels way too specific to just be a coincidence. don't you think it's possible that some objects just hold onto the energy of what's coming?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
